/* GOOGLE */
export const GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID = process.env.REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID

/* GOOGLE */
export const FACEBOOK_APP_ID = process.env.REACT_APP_FACEBOOK_APP_ID
/* API */
export const API_BASE_URL = process.env.REACT_APP_BASE_URL || 'http://localhost:3001'
export const API_LOGIN = API_BASE_URL + '/api/login'
export const API_SIGN_UP = API_BASE_URL + '/api/sign-up'
export const API_SOCIAL_LOGIN = API_BASE_URL + '/api/social-login'
export const API_USER_PROFILE = API_BASE_URL + '/api/profile'
export const API_FILE_UPLOAD = API_BASE_URL + '/api/file'
